{
  "signal_description": "The query retrieves the month, number of invoices, and average cycle time for each month. It uses the 'defaultview-225' table. The 'Month' column is derived by truncating the 'END_TIME' column to the month level. The 'No. of Invoices' column is calculated by counting the distinct values in the 'Inv. Accounting Document Number' column. The 'Avg. Cycle time' column is calculated by subtracting the last 'end_time' value for 'Clear Invoice' events from the first 'end_time' value for 'Post Invoice' events. The query filters the events to only include 'Post Invoice' and 'Clear Invoice' events. The results are ordered by the 'Month' column in ascending order and filled with missing months using a time series of 'MONTH'."
}
